-- Madrid Exchange Says 10 Stocks Were Affected by Technical Issue
-- B y   A l e x i s   X y d i a s   a n d   N a n d i n i   S u k u m a r
-- 2013-01-18T11:55:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-18/madrid-exchange-says-10-stocks-were-affected-by-technical-issue.html
A technical issue forced the Madrid
stock exchange to suspend trading in 10 stocks, including  Banco
Bilbao Vizcaya Argentaria SA (BBVA)  and  Sacyr Vallehermoso SA. (SYV)   Trading will resume after an auction scheduled for 12:50
p.m. local time, according to a spokesman for Bolsas y Mercados
Espanoles, who asked not to be identified.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alexis Xydias at 
 axydias@bloomberg.net  